Text: ...Out of the way.
Now then, if you don't want to die, make way.

N-No! How about you try being Lady Eta's assistant
instead?!
That's...also a no from me!
Lie down and stay down.
Eeeek...

Hmph... These rebels are nothing more than a motley
crew hastily thrown together at the last minute.

It's always that damn No. 93! I wish I could smash
that beautiful face of hers!
Are you praising her or insulting her...?
All jesting aside, their defense is solid.

Yes, and they're not only strategically weakening
our forces but are also concentrating their efforts
on No. 93 to undermine us.

Even among our members, the ruthlessness of No. 93
is well known—

Just her presence on the battlefield is enough to
dampen our morale.

Plus, the fact that Lady Gamma is taking command is
a significant factor.

To be precise, the fact that she's not on the
frontlines but providing rear support is enhancing
the unity of the troops on the frontline.
How does that...even...make sense...?!

Whether it makes sense or not, the reality is that
it's working.

Given the pressure No. 93 is exerting on the
battlefield, we need to figure out some sort of
countermeasure—
...No need for that.
Lady Eta?
I'll start the experiment...

...Lady Eta! Please drop your weapons and surrender
now!
Do it now, and Lady Alpha may still show you mercy!

We will not...surrender. We will break through your
defense lines.
We will secure the budget and personnel...!
Lady Eta...!

...In that case, we will have no choice but to
resort to force.
Think you'll be able to?
It's Lady Alpha's orders!
Thirty seconds have passed... Go, slime...
What?!

...What's this...?! My slime suit's composition
is...fluctuating?!
What's happening? I can't control it properly!
What's up...with No. 93's movements?!
Lady Eta...did you do something?
Yes, I did.

The micro-vibrations in this slime disrupt the flow
of magic and inhibit the composition of the
opponent's armor at a structural level.

It takes time to activate after being placed,
but the effects are outstanding...!

I want to improve it in the future to use it
anytime, anywhere, like a barrier... Hehehe...!

Disrupting the composition of the armor at the
structural level means that...

If this continues, No. 93's slime suit won't be able
to maintain its shape and will...fall off!?
Eeeeeek! What is that?!

I didn't hear anything from Lady Gamma about Lady
Eta going that far!
When I go, I go all the way.

I will secure the budget and strip you of your slime
suit.
I won't hurt you...
Nooooooo!!!
I'm sorry, Lady Gamma! I must retreat!!!

She's fled... Too bad. She would have made for an
excellent test subject.
...Magnificent, Lady Eta.

An attack that aims to destroy an opponent's armor
along with their dignity... How terrifying...!
Trust you to pull off something like that...

Alright, who's next? Anyone else brave enough to
step up?

Lady Eta, please be cautious! If No. 93 has been
systematically eliminated, then next will definitely
be—
Grrraaaaaaahhh!!!
Woooshrrraaahhh! All of you are my prey!
